## What was committed (3 files)

1. pnpm-lock.yaml (+~3500): the committed lockfile had ZERO @google/adk
   entries even though package.json on THIS commit declares @google/adk
   ^1.2.0 (L182) and lodash ^4.17.21 (L191, devDep for the lodash-es jest
   mapping). The lockfile was never regenerated when those deps were added,
   so CI frozen-lockfile install was BROKEN on this branch. The regen is
   purely additive (@google/adk's transitive tree: Azure / Google-Cloud /
   grpc / mikro-orm / pg / mariadb / a2a-js / ...). The 102 '-' lines are
   pnpm re-resolutions, NOT deletions — e.g. swagger-typescript-api 13.9.3 ->
   13.9.3(encoding@0.1.13) because `encoding` now enters the tree; every
   removed package still resolves in the new lockfile (verified by grep).

2. googleAdk.ts — plugin-core behavior fixes:
   - closeShortCircuitedModelSpan + modelSpanKeyForEvent: when a before-model
     callback returns a cached LlmResponse, ADK SKIPS afterModelCallback, so
     the yielded event is the only signal to close the chat span. Without it
     the chat span dangled and was marked interrupted. (This is exactly the
     behavior the discarded AGENTS.md bullet described — the fix lives in code
     now, so the doc bullet was redundant.)
   - recordEventError + applyRootError + InvocationState.rootErrorType/Message:
     propagate event.errorCode/errorMessage onto the root invoke_agent span
     (previously only the chat span carried the error).
   - beforeExit hook refactor: per-instance `beforeExitRegistered` flag ->
     module-level BEFORE_EXIT_CLEANUPS Set + per-instance beforeExitCleanup,
     plus unregisterBeforeExitHookIfIdle / runBeforeExitCleanups /
     unregisterBeforeExitHookIfUnused. Completed invocations now REMOVE their
     cleanup so a long-lived process creating many plugins doesn't leak one
     'beforeExit' listener per instance.
   - childContext + root startSpan now use ROOT_CONTEXT instead of
     otelContext.active() (the `context as otelContext` import was dropped):
     parent off the explicit root, not ambient context.
   - Expanded usage docstring + clarifying comments in toJsonSafe /
     systemInstructionParts (no behavior change).

3. googleAdk.test.ts (+64): root span ERROR status on model error; new
   'closes chat spans when beforeModelCallback returns a cached response';
   new 'completed invocations unregister their beforeExit cleanup' (asserts
   <=1 net beforeExit listener after 12 plugin lifecycles).

